        <content><![CDATA[<p>The <a href="%(link0)">Form-based content editor</a> and also the <a href="%(link1)">Inline content editor</a> are based on widgets. For each input field in the editor, a special widget is configured that defines how a value can be set. The available widgets reach from check boxes and select boxes up to very advanced image selection or location picker widgets. Here you get an overview on the available widgets and learn how to configure them.</p>]]></content>
